TI  - Limits of Transferring User-Defined Quantity Takeoff Rules in 2D CAD and 3D BIM Using Semantic Vertices
T2  - APPLIED SCIENCES-BASEL
LA  - English
KW  - dimension
KW  - quantity takeoff
KW  - 2D CAD
KW  - 3D BIM
