TI  - Exploring emerging barriers to BIM adoption for sustainable project tracking and control readiness in Saudi Arabia: an ISM-based approach
T2  - ENGINEERING CONSTRUCTION AND ARCHITECTURAL MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Project tracking
KW  - Monitoring and control
KW  - Sustainable projects
